# Files in this list are "hardened" — they have outsized blast radius and have
# repeatedly cost real debugging time when touched casually (measurement drift,
# layout cascades, reconciler miscommits, etc.).
#
# To commit a change that touches any of these paths, the commit message MUST
# contain the token `[hardened-ok]`. Enforced by .git/hooks/pre-commit,
# installed via scripts/install-hooks.
#
# One path per line. Comments (# prefix) and blank lines ignored. Patterns are
# exact prefix matches against the staged paths (e.g. `framework/gpu/` blocks
# any file under that directory).

framework/gpu/text.zig
framework/gpu/gpu.zig
framework/layout.zig
framework/text.zig
framework/engine.zig
framework/reconciler.zig
renderer/hostConfig.ts
build.zig
